%% Semantic search sequence - a natural-language product search request.
%% Source of truth: packages/web/app/products/_components/product-search.tsx,
%% packages/api/src/features/products/{products.routes.ts,products.service.ts},
%% packages/api/src/shared/embeddings/embeddings.service.ts, docs/adr/010-semantic-search.md.
%% Regenerate the SVG with: bun run diagrams
%%{init: { "sequence": { "width": 260 } } }%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor U as Browser
  participant W as web<br/>Next.js Server Components
  participant A as api<br/>Express
  participant OAI as OpenAI<br/>text-embedding-3-small
  participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>pgvector

  Note over U,DB: Products are embedded once<br/>at seed time (prisma/seed.ts) -<br/>see ADR 010. This sequence<br/>covers a live search request.

  U->>U: types query, ProductSearch<br/>debounces 400ms
  U->>W: client nav to /?q=...<br/>(drops page, sort, category)

  W->>A: GET /products?q=...
  A->>A: ProductListQuerySchema parses q,<br/>routes to searchProducts (not listProducts)
  A->>OAI: embeddings.create(input: q)

  alt embedding call fails
    OAI-->>A: error
    A-->>W: 500 (existing error middleware)
    W-->>U: error page
  else embedding succeeds
    OAI-->>A: 1536-dim vector
    A->>DB: ORDER BY embedding <=> vector<br/>WHERE embedding IS NOT NULL LIMIT 16
    DB-->>A: top 16 ranked products
    A-->>W: results, total, page 1, totalPages 1
    W-->>U: renders ProductSearch + ranked cards<br/>(category filters, sort, pagination hidden)
  end
